description: Try our easy to follow Crumbed Fish Lettuce Tacos recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
name: Crumbed Fish Lettuce Tacos Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Preheat oven to 180Â°C. Bake fish for 20 minutes or until cooked through.

Place avocado in a bowl, squeeze in lime to taste and set aside. Cook corn kernels in a nonstick frying pan until brown and set aside. Combine onion, tomato and coriander in a bowl. Season with pepper.

To assemble tacos, slice and place fish fillets, avocado and a scoop of tomato salsa into each lettuce cup. Squeeze with extra lime juice and serve with additional side salad. Season with Sriracha if desired.
